{"id":181015,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/09/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011922/","date":"2011-09-23T05:30:31Z","modified":"2011-09-23T05:30:31Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐 &#8211; 2011/9/22","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b></span><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/yigroup\">@yigroup</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/xiaomi2020\">@xiaomi2020</a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【时政热点】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/cifamerica/2011/sep/22/china-world-economic-saviour\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国有机会成为我们的救世主</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国已经失去了从经济危机中拯救世界的能力，如今只有中国有这样的资源，但要看她是否愿意了。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国节奏博客：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thechinabeat.org/?p=3819\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《谁害怕中国：中国软实力的挑战》节选</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“当人们表示或分析对中国崛起的恐惧时，很多时候并没有探讨其背后的深层原因”</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/british-columbia/chinese-trial-for-homicide-in-canada-breaks-new-legal-ground/article2175393/?utm_medium=Feeds%3A%20RSS%2FAtom&#038;utm_source=Asia-Pacific&#038;utm_content=2175393\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">加拿大杀人案在中国审理，开了法律先河</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——凶犯是华人，逃回国后被捕；加拿大要求遣返未果，在中国保证不判凶犯死刑后，将证据移交中国</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21530166\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国选秀节目：不许投票，我们是中国人！</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——有人认为，观众的投票是促使政府决心终止“快女”的主要原因</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21530162\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国售台武器问题：小心翼翼的舞蹈</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——美国要在过去的承诺与当前的要务之间寻找到某种平衡。它明白台湾的独立就意味着战争</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/flashpoints-blog/2011/09/22/cyber-revenge-against-japan/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对日本的网络报复？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——随着九一八的临近，中国网民中间出现了对日本发起网络攻击的呼吁，而三菱重工被黑客攻击事件恰在此时发生</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【国际外交】</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《经济学人》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.economist.com/node/21530102\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亚洲的芳心属谁家？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——</span></span><span><span>60</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年前的旧金山对日合约奠定了战后亚洲的基本阵营和格局，时至今日，当年刀兵相见的中美两国在经济上却是极为紧密的交缠在了一起</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/china-power/2011/09/22/to-interfere-or-not-to-interfere/?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+the-diplomat+%28The+Diplomat+RSS%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">干涉，还是不干涉？</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在公开场合，中国外交官依然宣称不干涉别国内政的方针，但是对利比亚局势和对苏丹公投的反应，说明这一方针并非一成不变</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【经济金融】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">市场观察：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.marketwatch.com/story/chinas-big-four-banks-reportedly-see-big-outflows-2011-09-22\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国四大银行面临储蓄流失现象</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——据一份报告显示，九月以来，中国四大银行的储蓄额下降了</span></span><span><span>4200</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿元人民币，这些钱很可能流入了民间借贷系统</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-09-22/yuan-options-turn-more-bearish-on-global-slump-china-credit.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">因全球经济不振，人民币交易前景变熊市</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——人民币已和世界经济发展结合在一起，一旦全球出现危机，唯一的货币避难所只有美元</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《金融时报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.ft.com/beyond-brics/2011/09/22/traders-prepare-for-falling-renminbi/#axzz1Ycy0Si8Y\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">外汇交易者为人民币贬值做准备</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在无本金交割远期外汇交易市场上，人民币呈贬值趋势。人们怀疑国际国内形势会使中国停止让货币升值。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110922/bs_nm/us_global_economy\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">欧美经济不景气，使得中国制造业速度放缓——</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">汇丰银行的中国采购经理指数表明，中国制造业已连续三月萎缩。虽然出口前景不好，但国内需求坚挺</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【生活百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《每日电讯报》：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/asia/china/8780976/China-suffering-from-Confucian-confusion-over-sex.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在性</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的问题上</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">，中国</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">面临</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“儒家困</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">境</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">”</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——在中国，表面上色情是非法的，但中国生产了全球</span></span><span><span>70%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的性用品，而政府也默许了很多色情活动</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社：</span></span><span><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://old.news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110922/ap_on_re_as/as_china_shark_fins\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">姚明与布莱森联手反对鱼翅贸易</span></a></span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——每星期有</span></span><span><span>150</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">万条鲨鱼被杀，</span></span><span><span>95%</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的鱼翅销往中国。中国人对鲨鱼翅的兴趣，使得鲨鱼面临被杀绝的危险。</span></span><span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span><span> </span></span></p>\n<div><i>发送邮件至 yyyyiiii+subscribe@googlegroups.com 即可订阅译文；译者的音频博客已登录iTunes，到<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/id453722327?ign-mpt=uo%3D4\">这里</a>即可收听往期的译者音频节目；下载更新需翻墙。</i><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/5425822223623422432-2394779386586792108?l=yyyyiiii.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=